Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.61,0:24:36.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,0)}塔奇克马式的日常
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.72,0:24:38.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家 吃惊吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.00,0:24:42.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少佐居然给我们送了礼物哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.85,0:24:43.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs50}第一弹 CHOCO SURPRISE
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.85,0:24:43.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs50}各种意义上来说都很危险哦？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.38,0:24:46.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 不想要吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.96,0:24:50.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是想引人注目 刚才那种谎话也…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.72,0:24:50.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本没可信度嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.34,0:24:52.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇呀！才没骗人呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.78,0:24:55.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下就算你们想要 我也绝对不会给你们的！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.70,0:24:59.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fs50}这个盒子里
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.70,0:24:59.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fs50}第一号
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.70,0:24:59.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fs50}鸵鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.70,0:24:59.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fs50}藏在里面哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.71,0:25:01.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我开动了



